35:10.342 --> 35:11.741
I gave you my word that I

35:11.743 --> 35:14.678
would come here
and record you.

35:15.214 --> 35:16.947
But if you think  that

35:16.949 --> 35:19.382
I'm gonna sign some
legal mumbo jumbo,

35:19.384 --> 35:21.084
then you are a lot crazier
than I thought

35:21.086 --> 35:22.719
you already were. (CHUCKLES)

35:22.721 --> 35:24.054
Mr. Melcher,
it was just...

35:24.056 --> 35:26.490
No one is gonna put a song

35:26.492 --> 35:30.160
about eating garbage
on the radio.

35:30.462 --> 35:31.728
No one.

35:31.730 --> 35:34.297
You can't write.
You can't sing.

35:34.299 --> 35:36.733
You certainly can't
play the guitar.

35:36.735 --> 35:39.136
I don't ever want
to hear from you again.

35:39.538 --> 35:41.605
And neither does Dennis.

35:51.884 --> 35:54.451
Charlie, I can, uh...
I can fix this.

35:54.453 --> 35:58.421
I had some money hidden away
from the Nixon campaign.

35:58.423 --> 36:01.658
If I can just get
to it, I can fix it.

36:11.870 --> 36:13.203
Run.

36:38.830 --> 36:40.897
You could
talk to him.

36:42.334 --> 36:44.134
What would I say?

36:44.203 --> 36:48.672
He's spent his whole life
wondering who you are,

36:48.674 --> 36:49.673
trying to picture you,

36:49.675 --> 36:51.708
trying to figure out
what he is.

36:53.078 --> 36:55.111
Meeting me won't help.

36:55.681 --> 36:59.849
But you may not get another
chance. You're his father.

37:01.420 --> 37:03.253
I killed his father.

37:06.458 --> 37:07.991
Am I free to go?

37:22.374 --> 37:23.773
Charmain.

37:28.847 --> 37:30.213
Charmain.

37:35.754 --> 37:37.887
Come here.
No!

37:39.558 --> 37:40.123
Young Miss Tully,

37:40.125 --> 37:43.126
whatever Kellaher offered you,
you should take it.

37:43.128 --> 37:45.095
They're coming
for my head either way,

37:45.097 --> 37:47.230
so some good
should come of it.

37:49.034 --> 37:51.768
Thank you
for your permission.

37:52.137 --> 37:53.770
But I don't need it.

37:54.873 --> 37:56.373
You don't need it.

37:57.409 --> 37:59.476
You're sloppy and vindictive

37:59.478 --> 38:02.212
and self-destructive,

38:02.214 --> 38:03.113
and this whole time,

38:03.115 --> 38:04.381
you've thought maybe
if I'm a good girl,

38:04.383 --> 38:06.116
you'll gift me your job
when you're done with it.

38:06.118 --> 38:09.653
Well, you're done with it,
whether you know it or not,

38:09.655 --> 38:11.688
and I don't want your job.

38:11.690 --> 38:12.689
I don't want your boss's job.

38:12.691 --> 38:15.191
I want the
Commissioner's job.

38:16.428 --> 38:17.694
So no.

38:17.696 --> 38:18.995
I don't need your permission

38:18.997 --> 38:21.665
to tell the truth
to Internal Affairs.

38:22.668 --> 38:24.901
You know,
sometimes I wonder,

38:24.903 --> 38:27.137
did I create the monster

38:27.139 --> 38:30.140
or did I just drag it
back from the swamp?

38:45.524 --> 38:47.023
(CHUCKLES)

38:49.895 --> 38:51.161
Ken.

38:51.930 --> 38:55.265
No one knew where you were.
I was worried, I...

38:55.267 --> 38:57.200
Thought something might have
happened to you.

38:57.202 --> 38:58.468
Sure you were.

38:58.470 --> 39:00.003
You were struck dumb with the

39:00.005 --> 39:02.472
thought of my slowly
decaying corpse.

39:02.541 --> 39:05.475
Spare me the bull.
What do you want here?

39:06.378 --> 39:07.944
A divorce.

39:10.449 --> 39:13.416
Your father crawled
out of his carapace

39:13.418 --> 39:15.485
and offered you up
to a new host?

39:15.487 --> 39:17.354
You always had
a way with words.

39:17.356 --> 39:18.388
You can tell your new suitors

39:18.390 --> 39:20.423
you're gonna become
a grandmother.

39:26.531 --> 39:29.032
You took Emma
from the hospital.

39:29.034 --> 39:30.433
Yes, I did.

39:32.337 --> 39:33.870
Good for you, Ken.

39:35.207 --> 39:37.540
You figured out
how to be a father...

39:38.610 --> 39:40.844
(SCOFFS)
Just in time.

39:43.982 --> 39:46.816
(DOOR OPENS AND CLOSES)

40:00.098 --> 40:01.731
(KEYBOARD CLACKING)

40:13.912 --> 40:15.278
What's up?

40:16.248 --> 40:17.480
Taking my 20.

40:17.482 --> 40:19.149
CUT: (SCOFFS)
Like hell you are.

40:19.151 --> 40:22.218
Accept it or not.
It won't change anything.

40:23.622 --> 40:24.788
What are you doing?

40:24.790 --> 40:27.924
I'm done, Cut.
I quit.

40:29.127 --> 40:30.460
You quit?

40:30.662 --> 40:32.662
Give my love
to Jeannie.

40:41.907 --> 40:44.741
Can anybody give
me a ride home?

41:36.361 --> 41:39.729
WOMAN (SOBBING)
Please... Please...

41:39.731 --> 41:40.597
Please help me, please!

41:40.599 --> 41:43.666
MAN: Stay down!
WOMAN: Please help me!
Please help me!

41:43.869 --> 41:44.934
WOMAN: (SCREAMS)

41:44.936 --> 41:46.503
Please, help me!
Please, help me!

41:46.505 --> 41:47.971
Please.
Please, take the baby out.

41:47.973 --> 41:51.174
Please just take
the baby out!

41:51.176 --> 41:53.576
Please, please, please!

41:54.279 --> 41:55.912
Please let my baby...
(SCREAMING)

41:55.914 --> 41:58.815
(STABBING)
(WOMAN CONTINUES SCREAMING)
